    <title>Dennis&#39; Journey</title>
    <url>/2024/08/31/Dennis-Journey/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="Introduction-The-Beginning"><a href="#Introduction-The-Beginning" class="headerlink" title="Introduction: The Beginning"></a>Introduction: The Beginning</h2><ul>
<li>這篇文章用以紀錄求學生涯中的點滴，當時的情緒、當時的細節，讓逐漸離我遠去的青春時光能有載體。</li>
<li>最重要的是此段經歷下的收穫與反思，是否能夠做的更好呢?試著引起我的思考，試著品嘗生活的細膩，試著跨越那些過不去的坎，並且能夠原諒自己，最終能好好地凝視未來，對於過錯雲淡風輕而非鑽牛角尖，正視錯誤並慢慢改正，朝著幸福持續邁進。<span id="more"></span></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Chapter-1-Childhood-and-Elementary-School"><a href="#Chapter-1-Childhood-and-Elementary-School" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 1: Childhood and Elementary School"></a>Chapter 1: Childhood and Elementary School</h2><h2 id="Chapter-2-Middle-School-Years"><a href="#Chapter-2-Middle-School-Years" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 2: Middle School Years"></a>Chapter 2: Middle School Years</h2><h2 id="Chapter-3-High-School-Life"><a href="#Chapter-3-High-School-Life" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 3: High School Life"></a>Chapter 3: High School Life</h2><h2 id="Chapter-4-University-Journey"><a href="#Chapter-4-University-Journey" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 4: University Journey"></a>Chapter 4: University Journey</h2><h2 id="Chapter-5-Looking-Forward"><a href="#Chapter-5-Looking-Forward" class="headerlink" title="Chapter 5: Looking Forward"></a>Chapter 5: Looking Forward</h2>]]></content>
